es/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但嗰邊應該都無濕熱嘅香港咁熱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:22:06.000Z","msg":"九月尾去仲熱唔熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d51fb71ee59d6b203606fe9e99429267fb85a8a1","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"45e36e1c943cd326b218597d04690d0c30be5bd3","tid":1350340,"uid":166388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d15c7ef91516f9d6c4cd8f7baa412d1f29148dd1","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T13:10:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x7y0KrA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx7y0KrA.png&h=47aedfcc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T16:49:45.000Z","msg":"哇ching你乾咗未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但嗰邊應該都無濕熱嘅香港咁熱？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T17:51:59.000Z","msg":"當你踩住單車嗰陣你啲汗就係濕熱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45e7514da5c41c64474408cc38a5886aab9a1554","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:10:22.000Z","msg":"講返第一日啲行程先<br />\n<br />\nEnschede-&gt;Zwolle-&gt;羊角村-&gt;Lelystad<br />\n<br />\n預九個至十二個鐘到<br />\n<br />\n其實踩到Zwolle已經攰，不過到羊角村唔知點解發瘟決定繼續踩60+k到Lelystad<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。嗰陣已經七點，超哂時。踩到Vollenhove(三分一左右)已經後悔想坐火車走，點知莫講火車，巴士都冇架。到嗰陣過八點所有超市準時收皮，冇水冇糧。<br />\n<br />\n繼續踩，過Shockland天橋嗰陣踩上高速公路俾人叫翻落去，落去嗰陣成架單車仆落水溝(荷蘭好多水溝)，半架車同手都係泥。過咗橋已經過十一點開始天黑開始淆，仲有成20k，嗰度係冇街燈。<br />\n<br />\n到一點天全黑，冇燈真係全黑，又勁多蟲撞向自己，入咗眼兩次。開始體力不支，有段路要抬單車上樓梯，幾乎冇力上(已經六個鐘冇水冇糧)。有段路踩錯另一邊，已兜遠路先去到，諗住直接剷過草地去，點知又有水溝<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，炒兩鑊。<br />\n<br />\n踩到一點幾仲有唯一一間McDrive未閂，喳喳林食完野去到兩點半先到訂咗嘅abnb"},{"pid":"ebd8976d2ed98f47de33e398f983467761139ca5","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T18:17:01.000Z","msg":"總結返第一日嘅戇鳩之處<br />\n<br />\n本身plan九個鐘已經係個錯誤，九個鐘係google map嘅九個鐘，我本身已經乘咗1.5落時間表到，不過都係太過高估自己。應該喺Zwolle留一日或者坐火車到Zwolle先開始踩。<br />\n<br />\nBackup plan係一事即刻直接坐火車走，不過喺第一日嘅行程唔得，因為全程得Hengelo, Zwolle, Lelystad有火車站<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。一個起點，一個自己戇鳩skip咗，一個終點。"},{"pid":"046ad40d4c544e14222d472a7497661c8489a107","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:14:00.000Z","msg":"依家已經第四日晚喺Utrecht<br />\n<br />\n等我補返第二三日先<br />\n<br />\n第二日skip咗Zaadam都係唔夠時間，踩完Volandam直接Purmerend坐火車到Amsterdam<br />\n<br />\nAmsterdam已經第三次去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GrVqXyO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGrVqXyO.png&h=3c6b3994&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最污糟嘅ah<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c80qXyP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc80qXyP.png&h=0d85d3b5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"71653a9c48c87d1b72f9e0a9a8bb80bf8e3959a1","tid":1350340,"uid":89452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:21:33.000Z","msg":"希望可以海外文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw祝巴打旅途愉快平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73b43342f328e9f4785c6dfabb87ca75bfe50660","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:27:54.000Z","msg":"第三日體力開始回復，最大問題係曬傷，好在有戴長袖外套遮住隻手<br />\n<br />\nAmsterdam-&gt;The Hague-&gt;Rotterdam<br />\n<br />\n十點Amsterdam出發<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/djOzQVh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdjOzQVh.png&h=83144cfe&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9cO8aVj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9cO8aVj.png&h=3082d8bb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0st4tG0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0st4tG0.png&h=fba8727c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zV6mvVn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzV6mvVn.png&h=e63e0ac5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/miH8Vm3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmiH8Vm3.png&h=2cc03c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踩到機場唞唞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/x8Rapfq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fx8Rapfq.png&h=54bf4e24&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6x5OaVr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6x5OaVr.png&h=83e2714f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n勁熱勁慢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j1WE12W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj1WE12W.png&h=9bcf207d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fKt8aWh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfKt8aWh.png&h=9885be7c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZrM5XBj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZrM5XBj.png&h=ebca6401&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n踩到海灘，有好多蘿莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uO78Vn1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuO78Vn1.png&h=47c6af78&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3OKGvWn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OKGvWn.png&h=f3eeed4c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O7zjhBp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO7zjhBp.png&h=a7064d0a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人生第一次比雀屎擊中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好溫<br />\n<br />\n全程最痛苦嘅時候，山坡又上又落，因為第一日嘅關係我膝頭痛到上唔到斜，一上斜坡就要推<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mVLnfn5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmVLnfn5.png&h=08d59f4f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wmcQpgs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwmcQpgs.png&h=e4365cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bmCwS9O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbmCwS9O.png&h=bca7f491&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n七點終於到The Hague，超時兩倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。又要坐火車到Rotterdam<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PhRBjPQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPhRBjPQ.png&h=28a73c42&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a56d91aada1285ec7d5f9a5861c633f32f78adae","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71653a9c48c87d1b72f9e0a9a8bb80bf8e3959a1","tid":1350340,"uid":89452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:21:33.000Z","msg":"希望可以海外文宣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBtw祝巴打旅途愉快平安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T19:29:03.000Z","msg":"覺得自己冇死真係奇蹟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有同自己Groupmate講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"710b45ed1d1bda57af0903f0c56ebd619ec056b0","tid":1350340,"uid":15595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:05:38.000Z","msg":"我唔會係live架下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家37 38度小心中暑呀<br />\n<br />\n利申喺amsterdam熱到唔想出街"},{"pid":"21cc995e8290a84afc464fbe6c4d14d7b56e1807","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"710b45ed1d1bda57af0903f0c56ebd619ec056b0","tid":1350340,"uid":15595,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:05:38.000Z","msg":"我唔會係live架下話？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家37 38度小心中暑呀<br />\n<br />\n利申喺amsterdam熱到唔想出街"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:33:36.000Z","msg":"Amsterdam<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />渣㗎，我要喺咁嘅地方40度連踩幾個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MZ3K0N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MZ3K0N.png&h=7340f596&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0b12dc4782cd6e0fa6e3cbb36ba229dde242d617","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:38:30.000Z","msg":"第四日係目前最滿意嘅一日，雖然都係好熱好攰，不過起碼踩晒全程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，七點幾到Utrecht仲有時間行下<br />\n<br />\n第四日嘅主題係heatwave，四十度踩六個鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。所以今日補給嘅次數特別多，每次經過超市就一定會入。<br />\n<br />\nRotterdam-&gt;Kinderdijk-&gt;Utrecht<br />\n<br />\n十點Rotterdam出發<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/piTj2Of.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpiTj2Of.png&h=bd854715&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u44WkzW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu44WkzW.png&h=d4ec6f98&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xXw9FzY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxXw9FzY.png&h=1d293e0a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2uoTnOj.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2uoTnOj.png&h=d8cfeaf1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5YntbGG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5YntbGG.png&h=4a684496&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vmVKuto.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvmVKuto.png&h=e19af140&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d5QVA8p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd5QVA8p.png&h=d8107c08&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n天橋踩錯方向俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uiM9Fz6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuiM9Fz6.png&h=87e91689&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g7yHf8s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg7yHf8s.png&h=059eb119&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/i4Ysse8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fi4Ysse8.png&h=56d8adc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一點到kinderdijk<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1vLnf83.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1vLnf83.png&h=7172bf71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db20811a4797bddf29cd8f95e675e3df2de7d5e1","tid":1350340,"uid":137233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T21:58:13.000Z","msg":"好在有lovelive歌陪住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd0e1bda2d9ec57bdee1fb1a888e5425db334ac9","tid":1350340,"uid":50831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:11:25.000Z","msg":"熱血吖！"},{"pid":"857934c11968f32d15855938e522de423267c73d","tid":1350340,"uid":59686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T22:12:03.000Z","msg":"我都係荷蘭 巴打聽日到邊"},{"pid":"18cb611a3